The Minuteman Can
 
We at The Modern Patriot believe that it is not only the right of Americans, but also the duty of all able-bodied citizens to maintain the readiness to form a militia and defend this nation against all enemies, foreign and domestic as stated in our constitution. This personal readiness, an act in self-reliance and liberty, is a combination of equipment, training, and mindset. It is our goal to build a community where all three of these things can be improved in every citizen that chooses to do so.
 
A major component of this personal readiness is the possession and maintenance of a semi-automatic battle rifle chambered in a sufficiently powerful round that can be easily found and exchanged with other Patriots. For the American people and our military, this duty has traditionally been placed on Eugene Stoners now infamous design, the AR-15. The rifle is simply a tool, machined metal and components that lie peacefully until picked up by a determined user.
 
The Minuteman Can is a simple ammo can that contains the bare essentials to keep an AR-15 running in tough situations. It can be stashed almost anywhere-behind the truck seat, the top of the closet, in the barn-and remain ready for when you need it. It’s nothing fancy – some industry leading magazines and federal ammunition, a field repair kit in case your rifle breaks down, and a cleaning kit to keep your rifle ready for duty. When your brothers and sisters call on you to stand beside them in battle, be sure that you have the necessary equipment to watch their six. Please recommend this product to your friends and family members; it gets hairy real fast when you’re out on the battlefield alone!
 
Packing List
(4) Magpul 30rd Pmags, gen 2 (black)
(300) Federal xm855 62gr 5.56x45 bullets
(1) Basic AR-15 field repair kit
(1) AR-15 cleaning kit
(1) Bottle CLP
(1) .50cal Ammo can
 
Please use common sense when storing this ammo can. Store in the safest way that your situation dictates in the driest, coolest place possible. Please keep out of reach of children, crazed liberals, and government officials. We cannot guarantee the integrity of this can or the ammunition for any amount of time as storage methods and climates will vary greatly. It is recommended that if you are unsure about the shelf-life of this can in the conditions you chose, replace it periodically to be sure everything is ready if you ever really need it.  Would like to sell FTF in the Hammond area or Northshore Area.  Thanks for reading!
The Modern Patriot, LLC

title: For Sale:  The Minuteman Can AR-15 battle pack
postcontent:
The Minuteman Can
 
We at The Modern Patriot believe that it is not only the right of Americans, but also the duty of all able-bodied citizens to maintain the readiness to form a militia and defend this nation against all enemies, foreign and domestic as stated in our constitution. This personal readiness, an act in self-reliance and liberty, is a combination of equipment, training, and mindset. It is our goal to build a community where all three of these things can be improved in every citizen that chooses to do so.
 
A major component of this personal readiness is the possession and maintenance of a semi-automatic battle rifle chambered in a sufficiently powerful round that can be easily found and exchanged with other Patriots. For the American people and our military, this duty has traditionally been placed on Eugene Stoners now infamous design, the AR-15. The rifle is simply a tool, machined metal and components that lie peacefully until picked up by a determined user.
 
The Minuteman Can is a simple ammo can that contains the bare essentials to keep an AR-15 running in tough situations. It can be stashed almost anywhere-behind the truck seat, the top of the closet, in the barn-and remain ready for when you need it. It’s nothing fancy – some industry leading magazines and federal ammunition, a field repair kit in case your rifle breaks down, and a cleaning kit to keep your rifle ready for duty. When your brothers and sisters call on you to stand beside them in battle, be sure that you have the necessary equipment to watch their six. Please recommend this product to your friends and family members; it gets hairy real fast when you’re out on the battlefield alone!
 
Packing List
(4) Magpul 30rd Pmags, gen 2 (black)
(300) Federal xm855 62gr 5.56x45 bullets
(1) Basic AR-15 field repair kit
(1) Ar-15 cleaning kit
(1) Bottle CLP
